0together%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20about%20470%20km%20after%20travelling%20at%20the%20same%20speed%20and%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20successful%20docking%20and%20undocking%20would%20make%20India%20the%20world's%20fourth%20nation%20to%20have%20space%20docking%20technology%2C%20ISRO%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20Dr%20Somnath%2C%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20multiple%20objects%20in%20space%20that%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20together%20for%20a%20specific%20purpose%2C%20a%20mechanism%20called%20docking%20is%20required.%20Docking%20is%20the%20process%20by%20which%20two%20space%20objects%20come%20together%20and%20connect%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20can%20be%20done%20using%20various%20approaches%20--%20soft%20mechanisms%2C%20hard%20mechanisms%2C%20or%20pressurised%20compartments%20for%20human%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20crew%20modules%20dock%20at%20the%20station%2C%20equalise%20pressure%2C%20and%20transfer%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%2099th%20rocket%20launch%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Centre%20of%20Sriharikota%20and%20it%20had%20a%20glorious%20lift%20off%2C%20placing%20SpaDeX%20satellites%20in%20the%20best%20orbit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20steps%20--%20docking%20and%20the%2024%20experiments%20--%20will%20be%20conducted%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20ISRO%2C%20which%20had%20started%202024%20with%20a%20PSLV%20launch%20on%20Jan%201%2C%20ends%20it%20on%20a%20high%20note%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735582680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fvp1hrqd8_isro-inspace-docking-_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-spadex-launch-for-in-space-