%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%20liable%20for%20sexually%20abusing%20and%20defaming%20writer%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20starting%20a%2030-day%20clock%20for%20her%20to%20receive%20the%20%245%20million%20jury%20award%2C%20plus%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exhaustive%2C%2077-page%20opinion%2C%20the%20US%20Second%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20rejected%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mimics-harvey-weinstein-arguments-e-jean-carroll-appeal-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20arguments%20brought%20by%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20seeking%20to%20overturn%20the%20May%202023%20trial%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Carroll%2C%20now%2081%20years%20old%2C%20shouldn't%20hold%20her%20breath.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Trump%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20president-elect%20plans%20to%20keep%20appealing%20the%20verdict.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20could%20keep%20the%20cash%20frozen%20well%20into%20next%20year%2C%20at%20least%2C%20legal%20experts%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%20and%20a%20half%20since%20the%20jury%20verdict%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-save-55000-on-5-million-e-jean-carroll-verdict-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%245%20million%20Trump%20owes%20Carroll%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20%24500%2C000%20to%20cover%20interest%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20sitting%20in%20an%20interest-bearing%20bank%20account%20controlled%20by%20the%20federal%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20does%20not%20file%20a%20further%20appeal%20in%20the%20next%2030%20days%2C%20the%20court%20will%20automatically%20transfer%20that%20%245.5%20million%20and%20any%20further%20interest%20directly%20to%20Carroll%20and%20her%20attorneys%2C%20said%20Nick%20Newton%2C%20a%20former%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Surety%20Bond%20Producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20and%20I%20are%20gra