erberg's%20fortune%20are%20both%20up%20significantly%2C%20and%20the%20company%20made%20headway%20on%20AI%2C%20hardware%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20a%20look%20back%20at%20the%20year%20for%20Meta%20and%20its%20chief%20executive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20was%20busy%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20allocated%20billions%20to%20keep%20Meta%20competitive%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20worked%20to%20thaw%20out%20a%20frosty%20relationship%20with%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20likely%20caused%20Apple%20to%20sweat%20over%20Meta's%20flashy%20smart%20glasses%20demo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20debuted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-new-look-haircut-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20look%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20many%20on%20social%20media%20applauded%20as%20more%20relatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20as%202024%20comes%20to%20a%20close%2C%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Meta%20have%20plenty%20of%20cause%20for%20celebration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20stock%20is%20up%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E66%25%20year-to-date%2C%20and%20Zuckerberg%20is%20more%20than%20%2484%20billion%20richer%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etoday%20than%20he%20was%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20reported%20an%20earnings%20beat%20in%20every%20quarter%20(though%20some%20were%20followed%20by%20brief%20stock%20drops)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-profits-first-ever-dividend-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclared%20its%20first-ever%20dividend%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20bird's-eye%20view%2C%20all%20in%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20successful%20year%20for%20Meta%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Minda%20Smiley%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20EMarketer%2C%20a%20sister%20company%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BDespi