g%2C%20satellite%20servicing%20and%20interplanetary%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%2025%20hour%20countdown%20which%20commenced%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20rocket%20lifted-off%20at%2010%20pm%20from%20the%20First%20Launch%20Pad%20at%20this%20spaceport%2C%20emanating%20thick%20orange%20coloured%20fumes%20and%20thunderous%20sound%20in%20the%20island%2C%20located%20about%20135%20km%20east%20of%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%20scientists%2C%20the%20two%20spacecraft-Spacecraft%20A%20(SDX01)%20or%20the%20'Chaser'%20and%20Spacecraft%20B%20(SDX02)%20or%20the%20'Target'%20would%20be%20merged%20together%20later%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20about%20470%20km%20after%20travelling%20at%20the%20same%20speed%20and%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20mastering%20the%20docking%20technologies%2C%20ISRO%20is%20set%20to%20enhance%20its%20operational%20flexibility%20and%20also%20expand%20its%20mission%20horizons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%20is%20essential%20for%20some%20of%20India's%20space%20ambitions%20like%20Indian%20on%20Moon%2C%20getting%20samples%20from%20the%20Moon%20(Chandrayaan-4%20mission)%2C%20building%20and%20operation%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Antariksh%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn-space%20docking%20technology%20is%20essential%20when%20multiple%20rocket%20launches%20are%20required%20to%20achieve%20common%20mission%20objectives.%20Through%20this%20mission%2C%20India%20is%20marching%20towards%20becoming%20the%20fourth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20have%20space%20docking%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20others%20to%20achieve%20this%20technological%20feat%20are%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Spacecraft%20has%20reached%20the%20desired%20orbit%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20scientists%20would%20take%20measures%20to%20merge%20the%20two%20by%20reducing%20the%20distance%20between%20them%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20the%20docking%20of%20the%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20PSLV-C60%20would%20be%20the%20last%20mission%20undertaken%20by%20the%20ISRO%20in%202024.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20began%202024%20with%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20PSLV-C58%2FXPOSAT%20mission%20on%20January%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20PSLV%20rocket%20also%20becomes%20the%20first%20vehicle%20to%20be%20integrated%20upto%20the%20fourth%20stage%20at%20the%20PSLV%20Integration%20Facility%20(PIF)%20that%20has%20been%20established%20at%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735578360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fqqee5bm8_spadex-mission_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launches-in-space-docking-experiment-from-sriharikota-7365585%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20spacecraft%20that%20would%20aid%20ISRO%20in%20demonstrating%20space%20docking%2C%20a%20critical%20technology%20for%20future%20space%20missions%20got%20separated%20successfully%20and%20were%20placed%20into%20the%20desired%20low%20earth%20orbit%20late%20on%20Monday%20night%2C%20ISRO%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launches-in-space-docking-experiment-from-sriharikota-7365585%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20to%20hold%20national%20day%20of%20mourning%20for%20Jimmy%20Carter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735577831000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ff0a7%2Flive%2F84305900-c6c6-11ef-8e21-f3ecf4ff8574.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp83p8pdg1xo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Th