with%20Mumbai's%20Mazagon%20Dock%20Shipbuilders%20under%20the%20'Atmanirbhar%20Bharat'%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20contracts%20have%20a%20combined%20value%20of%20Rs%202%2C867%20crore.%20While%20the%20contract%20with%20France's%20Naval%20Group%2C%20worth%20Rs%20877%20crore%2C%20pertains%20to%20more%20advanced%20torpedo%20technology%2C%20the%20contract%20with%20Mazagon%20Dock%2C%20worth%20around%20Rs%201%2C990%20crore%2C%20is%20over%20DRDO's%20new%20indigenous%20submarine%20propulsion%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20has%20signed%20two%20contracts%2C%20worth%20approximately%20Rs%202%2C867%20crore%2C%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20Air%20Independent%20Propulsion%20(AIP)%20Plug%20for%20DRDO-AIP%20system%20and%20its%20integration%20onboard%20Indian%20submarines%3B%20and%20the%20integration%20of%20electronic%20heavy%20weight%20torpedo%20(EHWT)%20onboard%20the%20Kalvari-class%20submarines%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20ministry%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDEAL%20WITH%20FRANCE'S%20NAVAL%20GROUP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20is%20about%20the%20Electronic%20Heavy%20Weight%20Torpedo%20or%20EHWT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20the%20deal%20for%20the%20integration%20of%20EHWT%20onboard%20the%20Kalvari-class%20submarines%20will%20be%20a%20joint%20effort%20by%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20the%20DRDO%20and%20Naval%20Group%2C%20France.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20greatly%20augment%20the%20firepower%20capabilities%20of%20Kalvari-class%20submarines%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20defence%20ministry%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Naval%20Group%2C%20the%20Electronic%20Heavy%20Weight%20Torpedo%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20F21%20Heavy%20Weight%20Torpedo%2C%20%26quot%3Bsuccessfully%20integrates%20the%20mastery%20of%20aluminum%20silver%20oxide%20technology%2C%20which%20greatly%20enhances%20the%20torpedo's%20range%20and%20allows%20for%20much%20higher%20speed.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20much%20more%20lethal%20weapon%20compared%20to%20other%20torpedoes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20feature%20of%20this%20torpedo%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20designed%20such%20that%20it%20can%20never%20explode%20on-board%20a%20submarine%20even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20fire%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20or%20if%20it%20is%20dropped%20of%20fired%20accidentally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDEAL%20WITH%20MAZAGON%20DOCK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20is%20about%20an%20advanced%20Air%20Independent%20Propulsion%20or%20AIP%20system.%20The%20AIP%20technology%20is%20being%20indigenously%20developed%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20or%20DRDO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20project%20pertains%20to%20construction%20of%20AIP-Plug%20and%20its%20integration.%20It%20will%20enhance%20the%20endurance%20of%20conventional%20submarines%20and%20significantly%20contribute%20towards%20the%20'Aatmanirbhar%20Bharat'%20initiative.%20It%20would%20generate%20employment%20of%20nearly%20three%20lakh%20man-days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20Independent%20Propulsion%20is%20a%20marine%20technology%20which%20allows%20a%20conventional%20or%20non-nuclear%20submarine%20to%20operate%20without%20access%20to%20atmospheric%20oxygen.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20allows%20the%20conventional%20submarine%20to%20stay%20submerged%20deep%20underwater%20without%20having%20to%20surface%20or%20use%20its%20snorkel%20for%20a%20much%20longer%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20snorkel%2C%20in%20submarine%20terminology%2C%20is%20a%20pipe%20that%20can%20reach%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20ocean%20while%20the%20submarine%20is%20at%20periscope%20depth%20to%20allow%20a%20proper%20air%20influx%20for%20the%20diesel%20engines.%20An%20AIP%20Plug%20can%20augment%20or%20replace%20the%20diesel-electric%20propulsion%20system%20of%20non-nuclear%20submarines.%20It%20is%20also%20called%20Air%20Independent%20Power%20as%20it%20allows%20for%20much%20longer%20underwater%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20agreements%20are%20under%20the%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%2C%20which%20means%20the%20propulsion%20system%20as%20well%20as%20the%20torpedoes%20will%20be%20manufactured%20in%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735576980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fprb90oik_submarine-at-mazagon-dock_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftorpedo-deal-with-french-firm-drdos-new-tech-to-boost-indias-submarines-7365532%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20signed%20two%20significant%20deals%20to%20greatly%20enhance%20its%20submarine%20fleet.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20deals%20was%20signed%20with%20France's%20Naval%20Group%2C%20the%20larger%20of%20the%20two%20contracts%20was%20signed%20with%20Mumbai's%20Mazagon%20Dock%20Shipbuilders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natasa-Hardik%2C%20Sania-Shoaib%3A%20Celeb%20divorces%20of%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735576356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116805237%2Cimgsize-41372.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnatasa-stankovic-and-hardik-pandya-sania-mirza-and-shoaib-malik-to-esha-deol-and-bharat-takhtani-celebrity-divorces-that-left-fans-shocked-in-2024%2Fphotostory%2F116805237.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116805237.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENatasa%20Stankovic%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Sania%20Mir