illegal%20activity%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20a%20benchmark%20of%20irresponsible%20and%20illegal%20behaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20kids%20and%20women%20are%20being%20kidnapped%20and%20assaulted%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20in%20Delhi%2C%20you%20have%20been%20occupied%20by%20pointless%20mudslinging%20and%20issuing%20instructions%20to%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20raids%20and%20inquiries%20on%20our%20leaders%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20actions%20have%20irreparably%20damaged%20the%20respect%20that%20people%20held%20for%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20have%20tarnished%20the%20legacy%20left%20behind%20by%20your%20predecessors%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20-%20who%20said%20he%20was%20writing%20in%20a%20personal%20capacity%20--%20had%20opened%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20much%20praise%2C%20commending%20her%20efficiency%20and%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20two-and-a-half-year%20tenure%20that%20I%20am%20seeing%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20discharge%20the%20duties%20of%20a%20Chief%20Minister.%20Your%20predecessor%20did%20not%20handle%20a%20single%20government%20department%20and%20never%20signed%20a%20file.%20In%20contrast%2C%20you%20are%20handling%20many%20departments%20and%20trying%20to%20tackle%20many%20governance%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20also%20expanded%20on%20his%20criticism%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20pointing%20to%20his%20description%20of%20Atishi%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20Chief%20Minister%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20such%20post%20in%20the%20Constitution%20and%20it%20is%20a%20reprehensible%20neglect%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Bab