2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20used%20to%20play%20like%20this%20only%20from%20day%20one.%20He%20will%20continue%20to%20make%20such%20mistakes.%20Tell%20me%20about%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%2C%20what%20have%20they%20doing%20since%20the%20last%2040-45%20innings%3F%20They%20should%20automatically%20sit%20outside%20if%20selectors%20are%20not%20doing%20it%20then%20they%20should%20do%20it%20themselves.%20You%20and%20I%20can't%20throw%20them%20out.%20The%20kind%20of%20form%20they%20are%20in%20then%20even%20if%20you%20will%20bowl%2C%20they%20will%20get%20out.%20I%20am%20saying%20this%20by%20experience.%20The%20shot%20which%20is%20their%20scoring%20one%2C%20why%20should%20not%20they%20play%3F%20David%20Gower%20and%20Gundappa%20Vishwanath%20scored%20so%20many%20runs%20by%20playing%20cut%20shots%2C%26quot%3B%20Surinder%20Khanna%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20has%20been%20struggling%20for%20form%2C%20and%20did%20all%20the%20hard%20work%20during%20the%20fifth%20day%20but%20eventually%20returned%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20with%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it.%20Instead%20of%20going%20all%20guns%20blazing%2C%20Rohit%20adopted%20a%20defensive%20stance%20and%20mustered%20up%20nine%20runs%20after%20facing%2040%20deliveries.%20After%20effectively%20dealing%20with%20the%20pace%20threat%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20on%20his%20counterpart%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20attempt%20to%20flick%20the%20ball%20away%20resulted%20in%20a%20thick%20outside%20edge%2C%20which%20carried%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Marsh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1425-mitchell-marsh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Marsh%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20gully.%20With%20his%20head%20and%20shoulders%20slumped%2C%20Rohit%20returned%20to%20the%20dugout%20and%20left%20the%20floodgates%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Rohit's%20dismissal%2C%20everything%20fell%20apart%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20joined%20the%20Indian%20skipper%20in%20the%20same%20over%20for%20a%20five-ball%20duck.%20Virat%20Kohli%20lost%20his%20discipline%20and%20got%20lured%20into%20playing%20a%20drive%20on%20the%20ball%20by%20left-armer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20final%20ball%20before%20lunch.%20Jaiswal%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%20offered%20stability%20and%20assurance%20by%20leading%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Australian%20bowling%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2068-year-old%20further%20said%20that%20if%20both%20of%20them%20continue%20to%20fail%2C%20then%20the%20selectors%20should%20take%20a%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20batters%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20are%20out%20of%20form%20and%20selectors%20need%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20If%20they%20are%20not%20announcing...then%20selectors%20need%20to%20announce%20something.%20Going%20into%20the%20next%20test%2C%20play%20youngsters%2C%20we%20will%20win%2C%20like%20under%20Bumrah%20we%20won%20the%20first%20Test.%20We%20outclassed%20Australia.%20Since%20Rohit%20came%20back%20we%20have%20been%20struggling.%20I%20may%20sound%20harsh%20but%20you%20have%20to%20take%20harsh%20decisions%20if%20you%20want%20to%20win.%20We%20watch%2C%20we%20cry...we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20say%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20cricketer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20for%20an%20unbeaten%20100%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20Perth%2C%20the%20Aussies%20have%20managed%20to%20keep%20Virat%20quiet%20as%20he%20has%20managed%20just%2026%20runs%20in%20his%20other%20four%20innings%2C%20including%