-newspaper-editor-steps-down-after-elon-musks-op-ed-backs-far-right-party%2Famp_articleshow%2F116804708.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Digi%20Yatra%20Data%20Being%20Used%20To%20Identify%20Tax%20Evaders%3F%20Centre%20Clarifies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20today%20refuted%20a%20report%20that%20said%20passengers'%20data%20from%20the%20Digi%20Yatra%20application%20was%20being%20used%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20tax%20evaders.%20%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20media%20report%20concerning%20Digi%20Yatra%20is%20based%20on%20unfounded%20and%20inaccurate%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20sharing%20of%20Digi%20Yatra%20passengers'%20data%20with%20Indian%20tax%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20denial%20comes%20after%20a%20newspaper%20report%2C%20citing%20sources%2C%20claimed%20the%20tax%20department%20had%20access%20to%20the%20Digi%20Yatra%20app%20data%20which%20was%20being%20reconciled%20with%20tax%20filings%20to%20check%20for%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20declared%20income.%20It%20added%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20would%20start%20issuing%20notices%20to%20tax%20evaders%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20informed%20that%20the%20app%20%26quot%3Bfollows%20the%20Self-Sovereign%20Identity%20(SSI)%20model%2C%20where%20Personally%20Identifiable%20Information%20(PII)%20and%20travel%20credentials%20are%20stored%20exclusively%20on%20the%20user's%20device%2C%20not%20on%20any%20central%20repository%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20hereby%20clarifies%20that%20the%20recent%20media%20report%20concerning%20Digi%20Yatra%20is%20based%20on%20unfounded%20and%20inaccurate%20claims.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20is%20no%20sharing%20of%20Digi%20Yatra%20passengers%20data%20with%20Indian%20tax%20authorities.%20The%20Digi%20Yatra%20app%20follows%20the%20Self-Sovereign%20Identity%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20MoCA_GoI%20(%40MoCA_GoI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoCA_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1873721428006031553%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20user%20uninstalls%20the%20Digi%20Yatra%20app%2C%20the%20data%20is%20deleted%20entirely%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20clarifying%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAirport%20systems%20automatically%20purge%20passenger%20data%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20the%20flight's%20departure.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20Digi%20Yatra%20is%20designed%20solely%20for%20domestic%20passengers%20and%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20international%20travellers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20also%20denied%20the%20report%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20not%20looking%20at%20Digi%20Yatra%20data%20to%20go%20after%20evaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20seen%20that%20news%20articles%20have%20appeared%20stating%20that%20Digiyatra%20data%20will%20be%20used%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20tax%20evaders.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20this%20connection%20it%20is%20clarified%20that%20as%20on%20date%20there%20is%20no%20such%20move%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIncomeTaxIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IncomeTaxIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20department.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnsitharamanoffc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40nsitharamanoffc%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FofficeofPCM%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40officeofPCM%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFinMinIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40FinMinIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D