s%2070%E2%80%9D%20which%20was%20shortlisted%20on%20Dec.%2017%20for%20the%2097th%20Oscars.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22John%20Hopewell%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmorena-films-a-contracorriente-films-noodles-productions-1236261852%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Row%20Over%20Maharashtra%20Minister's%20%26quot%3BKerala%20Mini%20Pak%26quot%3B%20Remark.%20He%20Clarifies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENitesh%20Rane%2C%20Maharashtra%20minister%20and%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%20has%20sparked%20another%20controversy%20calling%20Kerala%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini%20Pakistan%26quot%3B%20during%20his%20attempts%20to%20target%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Wayanad.%20Called%20out%20by%20the%20Opposition%2C%20he%20clarified%20that%20while%20Kerala%20is%20part%20of%20India%2C%20he%20compared%20it%20to%20Pakistan%20because%20of%20the%20incidents%20of%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20and%20religious%20conversions%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKerala%20is%20mini%20Pakistan%20that%20is%20why%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%20are%20elected%20from%20there.%20All%20terrorists%20vote%20for%20them.%20This%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20you%20can%20ask.%20They%20have%20become%20MPs%20after%20taking%20terrorists%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rane%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20earlier%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20leaders%20lost%20no%20time%20in%20condemning%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20else%20can%20one%20expect%20from%20Nitesh%20Rane%3F%26quot%3B%20fumed%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Atul%20Londhe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20do%20this%20only.%20However%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20The%20person%20(Nitesh%20Rane)%2C%20who%20is%20a%20minister%2C%20has%20taken%20an%20oath%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20(maintain)%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20unity%20of%20India.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20labelling%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20states%20as%20Pakistan.%20He%20is%20calling%20the%20voters%20there%20as%20'terrorists.'%20Should%20he%20have%20the%20right%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20ministerial%20position%3F%20This%20is%20my%20question%20to%20you%2C'%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20worried%20since%20PM%20Modi%20won%20only%20by%20a%20lakh%20votes%2C%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20digest%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20win%2C'%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Anand%20Dubey%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20matter%20snowballed%2C%20Mr%20Rane%20issued%20a%20clarification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKerala%20is%20very%20much%20part%20of%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20decreasing%20population%20of%20Hindus%20is%20something%20everyone%20should%20worry%20about.%20The%20religious%20conversion%20of%20Hindus%20into%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20(Islam%20and%20Christianity)%20has%20become%20an%20everyday%20thing%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rane%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversy.%20In%20September%2C%20he%20sparked%20a%20row%20with%20provocative%20speeches%20in%20which%20he%20allegedly%20threatened%20to%20hit%20Muslims%20and%20a%20police%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20had%20a%20defamation%20suit%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Sanjay%20Raut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navi%20Mumbai%20police%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20for%20allegedly%20using%20the%20word%20'Dalit'%20while%20speaking%20to%20a%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735568940000%2C%22visual%22%3A