20different%20ways%20of%20looking%20at%20something.%20But%20no%20matter%20how%20one%20sees%20it%2C%202024%20reveals%20to%20be%20uninspiring%20for%20Hindi%20films.%20Quantity%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20problem.%20Admittedly%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lull%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20crisis%2C%20but%20some%20time%20has%20passed%20and%20as%20of%20now%2C%20a%20steady%20roster%20of%20theatrical%20and%20streaming%20releases%20is%20in%20place.%20Theatre%20owners%20and%20exhibitors%20also%20came%20up%20with%20a%20ploy%20to%20combat%20infrequent%20releases%3A%20re-releasing%20old%20Hindi%20films.%20Yet%2C%20the%20quality%20has%20been%20on%20a%20steady%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Era%20Of%20'Genericness'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20landscape%20of%20Hindi%20films%20resembles%20a%20linear%20line%20drawn%20by%20a%20vanishing%20ink.%20The%20multi-crore%20industry%20has%20come%20to%20be%20imbued%20by%20such%20genericness%20in%20plot%20and%20aesthetics%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20locate%20its%20identity.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20long%20the%20line%20is%E2%80%94and%20how%20expansive%20the%20industry%20is%20becoming%E2%80%94the%20growth%20feels%20incidental%2C%20for%20the%20ambition%20is%20stunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20have%20been%20the%20post-pandemic%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20easy%20availability%20of%20other%20Indian%20language%20films%20through%20streaming%20sites%20during%20that%20period%2C%20or%20the%20gigantic%20successes%20of%20those%20ventures.%20In%202022%2C%20S.S.%20Rajamouli's%20%3Cem%3ERRR%20%3C%2Fem%3Eregistered%20the%20highest%20opening%20by%20an%20Indian%20film%3B%20this%20year%2C%20another%20Telugu%20language%20film%2C%20Sukumar's%20%3Cem%3EPushpa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20became%20the%20highest-grossing%20Indian%20film%20in%20the%20first%20week.%20But%20evidently%2C%20the%20monopoly%20of%20Hindi%20films%20and%20its%20false%20equivalence%20with%20Indian%20cinema%20have%20considerably%20weakened.%20The%20diversity%20of%20the%20industry%20has%20been%20steamrolled%20into%20a%20prickly%20homogeneity%20where%20any%20two%20films%20look%20the%20same%2C%20the%20scale%20feels%20identical%2C%20the%20action%20looks%20uniformly%20designed%20and%20the%20style%20is%20fashioned%20in%20self-reflexive%20humour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20often%20the%20case%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20paved%20the%20way.%20His%202023%20film%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%20%3C%2Fem%3Enot%20just%20marked%20his%20return%20to%20the%20screen%20after%20a%20four-year%20hiatus%20but%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20outings%20that%20earned%20money%20at%20a%20time%20many%20others%20struggled%20to%20do%20so.%20Its%20success%20did%20three%20things%3A%20it%20reiterated%20the%20supremacy%20of%20Khan%2C%20legitimised%20action%20as%20a%20thriving%20genre%2C%20and%20recognised%20star%20cameos%20in%20films%20as%20the%20onset%20of%20multiverses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpectacle%20Over%20Everything%20Else%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20most%20Hindi%20films%20can%20be%20slotted%20in%20these%20distinct%20categories.%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20his%20version%20of%20a%20(cop)%20multiverse%2C%20and%20the%20production%20house%20Maddock%20Films%20furthered%20its%20horror-comedy%20universe%20with%3Cem%3E%20Stree%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EMunjya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Sagar%20Ambre%20and%20Pushkar%20Ojha%20helmed%20the%20action-thriller%20%3Cem%3EYodha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Siddharth%20Anand%20directed%20the%20aviation%20(action)%20thriller%3Cem%3E%20Fighter%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Ali%20Abbas%20Zafar%20made%20the%20abysmal%20%3Cem%3EBade%20Miyan%20Chote%20Miyan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3EBMCM%3C%2Fem%3E).%20There%20are%20more%20examples%3A%20Nikkhil%20Advani%20leaned%20on%20action%20with%20%3Cem%3EVedaa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ravi%20Udyawar%20did%20the%20same%20with%20%3Cem%3EYudhra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20so%20did%20Aditya%20Datt%20in%20%3Cem%3ECrakk%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Clubbing%20them%20together%20could%20be%20reductive%2C%20but%20it%20is%20difficult%20not%20to%20identify%20the%20sweeping%20attempt%20by%20the%20makers%20to%20treat%20plot%20as%20an%20accessory%20to%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%2C%20meta%20references%20clog%20the%20screenplay.%20Khan's%20famous%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBete%20ko%20hath%20lagane%20se%20pehle%2C%20baap%20se%20baat%20kar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(%26quot%3BBefore%20touching%20the%20son%2C%20deal%20with%20the%20father%26quot%3B)%2C%20rooted%20to%20the%20personal%20turmoil%20of%20his%20son's%20arrest%20in%202021%2C%20spawned%20similar%20iterations%20post%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2023).%20Tiger%20Shroff%20repeated%20his%20meme-famous%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Echoti%20bachi%20ho%20kya%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(%26quot%3Bare%20you%20a%20little%20girl%26quot%3B)%20a%20decade%20later%20in%20%3Cem%3EBMCM%20%3C%2Fem%3Eafter%20mouthing%20them%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20%3Cem%3EHeropanti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2014)%3B%20Chitrangada%20Singh%20briefly%20appeared%20in%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20%3Cem%3EKhel%20Khel%20Mein%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2024)%20and%20their%20scenes%20were%20scored%20to%20the%20music%20of%20%3Cem%3EDesi%20Boyz%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2011)%2C%20the%20last%20film%20they%20did%20together.%20The%20subtext%20here%20is%20actors%20winking%20directly%20at%20the%20audience%20and%20establishing%20a%20connection%20despite%20the%20fourth%20wall.%20But%20Hindi%20films%20have%20never%20seemed%20more%20distant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStuck%20On%20Repeat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%202024%20proved%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20that%20what%20works%20really%20does%2C%20and%20when%20it%20does%2C%20it%20is%20repeated.%20The%20success%20of%20%3Cem%3EStree%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%3C%2Fem%3E%20furthered%20the%20accomplishment%20of%20sequels%2C%20and%20now%2C%20there%20are%20multiple%20in%20the%20works.%20The%20Ranbir%20Kapoor-starrer%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2023)%20ended%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%20Park%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20go%20on%20floors%20in%202027.%20Varun%20Dhawan%20is%20part%20of%20%3Cem%3ENo%20Entry%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EBorder%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20reportedly%20a%20sequel%20to%20%3Cem%3EJugjugg%20Jeeyo%3C%2Fem%3E%20too.%20Vikas%20Bahl's%20%3Cem%3EShaitaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20minted%20money%20this%20year%2C%20has%20a%20sequel%20in%20the%20making%2C%20and%20in%20October%2C%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20producer%20Sajid%20Nadiadwala%20confirmed%20working%20on%20%3Cem%3EKick%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20cheeky%20Instagram%20post.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20is%20rumoured%20to%20be%20featuring%20in%20%3Cem%3EPathaan%202%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20actor%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20is%20either%20working%20in%20a%20sequel%20or%20wants%20to%20be%20in%20one.%20It%20is%20a%20jarring%20trend%20that%20spells%20a%20creative%20crisis%20in%20Hindi%20cinema%20with%20a%20damning%20pronouncement.%20As%20of%20this%20moment%2C%20filmmakers%20are%20more%20involved%20in%20catering%20to%20the%20audience%20than%20creating%20for%20them.%20Budgets%20are%20being%20amped%20up%2C%20more%20investment%20is%20tailored%20for%20VFX%20and%20Hindi%20films%20are%20getting%20bigger.%20Yet%2C%20one%20would%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20distinguish%20between%20the%20trailers%20of%2C%20say%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBaby%20John%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20story%20everywhere%3A%20overgrown%20men%20fighting%20with%20an%20obscure%20vengeance%20to%20prove%20their%20manhood%20rather%20than%20seek%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBankruptcy%20Of%20Imagination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20this%20crystallises%20the%20most%20terrifying%20symptom%20of%20Hindi%20cinema%20today%20where%20the%20bankruptcy%20of%20imagination%20has%20manifested%20in%20accentuating%20machismo.%20More%20and%20more%20films%20centre%20around%20men%20who%20need%20an%20excuse%20to%20draw%20out%20blood%20from%20the%20next%20person.%20The%20face%20does%20not%20matter%2C%20nor%20does%20the%20cause.%20While%20they%20thumped%20about%20the%20screens%2C%20smaller%20and%20more%20inventive%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20Sanjay%20Tripaathy's%20warm%20%3Cem%3EBinny%20And%20Family%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Karan%20Gour's%20whimsical%20%3Cem%3EFairy%20Folk%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shoojit%20Sircar's%20affecting%20%3Cem%3EI%20Want%20to%20Talk%3C%2Fem%3E%20battled%20for%20more%20screens%20and%20our%20attention.%20Even%20Kiran%20Rao's%20wonderful%20%3Cem%3ELaapataa%20Ladies%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Varun%20Grover's%20perceptive%20%3Cem%3EAll%20India%20Rank%3C%2Fem%3E%20garnered%20appreciation%20once%20they%20landed%20on%20digital%20platforms.%20Once%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20referred%20to%20as%20multiplex%20films.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20too%20ambitious%20for%20streaming%20and%20too%20atypical%20for%20theatres.%20They%20reside%20in%20a%20no%20man's%20land%2C%20and%20in%20their%20dislocation%2C%20they%20mirror%20the%20gradual%20distortion%20of%20Hindi%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ishita%20Sengupta%20is%20an%20independent%20film%20critic%20and%20culture%20writer%20from%20India.%20Her%20writing%20is%20informed%20by%20gender%20and%20pop%20culture%20and%20has%20appeared%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20Hyperallergic%2C%20New%20Lines%20Magazine%2C%20etc.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735559040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fpu0aqui_m_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flaapata-bollywood-how-2024-became-the-year-of-banality-7363333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Budgets%20are%20getting%20amped%20up%2C%20more%20investment%20is%20tailored%20for%20VFX%20and%20Hindi%20films%20are%20getting%20bigger.%20Yet%2C%20one%20would%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20distinguish%20between%20the%20trailers%20of%20Baby%20John%20and%20Animal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flaapata-bollywood-how-2024-became-the-year-of-banality-7363333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thai%20Influencer%20Dies%20After%20Guzzling%20Whisky%20Bottles%20In%20Rs%2075%2C000%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Thai%20social%20media%20influencer%20has%20died%20after%20he%20drank%20two%20bottles%20of%20whisky%20as%20part%20of%20a%20bet.%20Thanakarn%20Kanthee%2C%20more%20popularly%20known%20online%20as%20%26quot%3BBank%20Leicester%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20offered%2030%2C000%20Thai%20baht%20(Rs%2075%2C228)%20to%20down%20the%20bottles%20as%20part%20of%20the%20challenge.%20The%2021-year-old%20regularly%20took%20on%20such%20challenges%20which%20previously%20included%20drinking%20hand%20sanitiser%20and%20wasabi%20in%20exchange%20for%20money.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20a%20birthday%20party%20in%20Tha%20Mai%20district%20of%20Chanthaburi%20on%20December%2025%20where%20Mr%20Kanthee%2C%20who%20had%20intellectual%20disabilities%2C%20arrived%20around%2011%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20party%2C%20Mr%20Kanthee%20was%20challenged%20to%20drink%20a%20350ml%20bottle%20of%20Regency%20whiskey%20with%20a%20cash%20offer%20of%2010%2C000%20baht%20per%20bottle%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FA%2520Thai%2520social%2520media%2520influencer%2520has%2520died%2520after%2520he%2520drank%2520two%2520bottles%2520of%2520whisky%2520as%2520part%2520of%2520a%2520bet.%2520Thanakarn%2520Kanthee%2C%2520more%2520popularly%2520known%2520online%2520as%2520%2522Bank%2520Leicester%2522%2C%2520was%2520offered%252030%2C000%2520Thai%2520baht%2520(Rs%252075%2C228)%2520to%2520down%2520the%2520bottles%2520as%2520part%2520of%2520the%2520challenge.%2520The%252021-year-old%2520regularly%2520