ens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20crucial%20for%20those%20managing%20pre-existing%20conditions%20like%20diabetes%20or%20hypertension%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20impact%20healthcare%20costs.%20Moreover%2C%20pre-existing%20illnesses%20can%20influence%20health%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20potentially%20resulting%20in%20higher%20costs%20or%20even%20denial%20of%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20aims%20to%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20senior%20citizens%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComprehensive%20Coverage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cardholders%20can%20receive%20cashless%20treatment%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20annually%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20covering%20an%20extensive%20range%20of%20medical%20procedures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20the%20extensive%20list%20of%20hospitals%20that%20come%20under%20the%20card%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2Fimg%2Fresources%2FPMJAY-Hospital-List.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInclusivity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unlike%20schemes%20that%20target%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups%2C%20this%20programme%20is%20universal%20for%20all%20citizens%20aged%2070%20and%20above%2C%20breaking%20socio-economic%20barriers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBeneficiaries%20can%20avail%20of%20treatments%20at%20any%20empanelled%20hospital%20nationwide%2C%20ensuring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333453%2Fkochi-startup-ansfrid-smartcare-emergency-alert-smart-watch-for-senior-citizens-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseamless%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20access%20even%20outside%20their%20home%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Apply%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Health%20Authority%20(NHA)%20has%20simplified%20the%20registration%20process%20for%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Vaya%20Vandana%20card.%20Seniors%20can%20now%20register%20in%20multiple%20ways%3A%20online%20through%20the%20beneficiary%20portal%20(beneficiary.nha.gov.in)%20or%20the%20Ayushman%20app%2C%20or%20in%20person%20at%20PM-JAY%20empanelled%20hospitals%20and%20common%20service%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEligible%20individuals%20can%20complete%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20e-KYC%20through%20the%20National%20Health%20Authority%20website%20or%20Common%20Service%20Centres%20(CSCs)%20to%20register.%20After%20successful%20verification%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20receive%20the%20card%2C%20granting%20them%20access%20to%20cashless%20treatment%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20commitment%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363871%2Fdr-ravinder-chowkidaar-sushruta-foundation-warangal-telangana-low-cost-free-surgery-healthcare-underprivileged%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20health%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20senior%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdi