-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D390926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%20twenty%20years%2C%20Paras%20Banjara%2C%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20fighting%20discrimination%2C%20securing%20vital%20documents%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20land%20ownership%20for%20Rajasthan's%20nomadic%20tribes.%20Through%20Olakhaan%20Trust%2C%20he%20aims%20to%20reclaim%20their%20lost%20identity%20and%20ensure%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society%2C%20giving%20nomadic%20voices%20the%20recognition%20and%20rights%20they%20deserve.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F390926%2Fparas-banjara-olakhaan-trust-nomadic-communities-rights-rajasthan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223500%2B%20Visually%20Impaired%20Individuals%20Can%20Now%20Lead%20Independent%20Lives%2C%20Thanks%20to%20This%20Pune%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Vision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThere%20are%20problems%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20solve%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThere%20are%20hindrances%20on%20the%20road%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20cross%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThere%20are%20difficulties%20in%20life%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20answer%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20spite%20of%20problems%2C%20hindrances%2C%20and%20difficulties%2C%20life%20is%20beautiful!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20pledge%20is%20how%20we%20start%20our%20days%20at%20Niwant%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Athang%20Bhandare%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20from%20Vadhu%20Bhudruk%20village%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Up%20until%20he%20was%2014%2C%20Athang%20studied%20in%20a%20regular%20school%2C%20with%20sighted%20children%2C%20but%20when%20his%20vision%20started%20to%20get%20bad%20soon%20after%2C%20he%20had%20to%20move%20to%20a%20school%20for