vernment%20support%2C%20the%20app%20has%20expanded%20its%20reach%2C%20including%20a%20Hindi%20version%20and%20plans%20to%20integrate%20it%20into%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Intelligence.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20West%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20a%20scribe.%20They%20teach%20touch%20typing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20adds.%20Through%20Swalekhan%2C%20Niwant%20is%20now%20helping%20reshape%20the%20future%20of%20visually%20impaired%20students%20in%20India%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20education%20without%20relying%20on%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiwant%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20intertwined%20with%20the%20Badve%20family%E2%80%99s%20dedication.%20Uma%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20dad%20turned%2060%2C%20he%20left%20his%20business%20and%20joined%20my%20mother.%20The%20number%20of%20students%20we%20had%20coming%20in%20grew%2C%20so%20it%20was%20good%20that%20along%20with%20the%20volunteers%20and%20teachers%2C%20she%20had%20more%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeera%20and%20her%20husband%20started%20by%20providing%20basic%20education%20and%20braille%20resources%20and%20then%20expanded%20to%20include%20classes%20for%20competitive%20exams%2C%20like%20banking%20and%20government%20jobs.%20Over%20200%20Niwant%20students%20are%20now%20employed%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20banking%20sector%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20quota%20for%20the%20visually%20impaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Miles%20to%20go%20before%20I%20sleep%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiwant%E2%80%99s%20unique%20model%20of%20learning%20and%20support%20has%20led%20to%20lasting%20relationships%20among%20its%20students.%20%E2%80%9CKids%20were%20coming%20in%20at%2011th%20grade%2C%20and%20we%20would%20help%20them%20until%20they%20got%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meera%20explains.%20Many%20students%2C%20who%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20Niwant%20for%20years%2C%20ended%20up%20marrying%20one%20another.%20%E2%8